text: John Moore (born July 31, 1964) is an American rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:American male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from New York City
